oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dragon's Concert Benefit for Nashville Children's Theatre (postcard)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Mosser, Jonell; McClinton, Delbert; Metal photoplates; Fund raising;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color postcard (green on white) announcing Dragon's Concert a benefit for the Nashville Children's Theatre featuring Jonell Mosser and special guest Delbert McClinton in Nashville, Tennessee on March 10. Poster features metal photoplates of Jonell Mosser and Delbert McClinton.
